# conversation.p0t — MULTI-TURN assertions (gen345).
# A section runs its `> / <` pairs in order against the same live brain, so state
# taught in one turn is visible to a later turn. (Mock / stub / flag / KB-state
# control are not part of this base — they come later.)

[test name-memory]
> my name is Francesco
< Nice to meet you, Francesco!
> what is my name
< Your name is Francesco.

[test follow-up-topic]
> what is the capital of italy
< Rome.
> what is the capital of japan
< Tokyo.